372
00:35:19,844 --> 00:35:21,596
Me fale sobre a casa.

373
00:35:21,679 --> 00:35:25,266
Tem armaduras sinistras ou quadros
de gente com os olhos recortados?

374
00:35:26,017 --> 00:35:27,977
Ou uma cripta no porão?

375
00:35:30,438 --> 00:35:31,564
É.

376
00:35:32,398 --> 00:35:33,650
Alô?

377
00:35:34,609 --> 00:35:35,693
Kate?

378
00:35:36,653 --> 00:35:37,904
